sub_title: Staff Writer at Jobsity | RFP & SEO Content Consultant
summary: I'm a business writer with nine years of full-time professional experience and a background in Business Management and HR. I specialize in grants, RFPs, B2B, and SEO optimization/content creation. Everyone has a voice worth hearing. My job is to organize your thoughts into words that will reach the perfect audience. Let's build your brand, win you that funding, and achieve your goals!
